## 📈 Key Insights

- Explored customer purchasing patterns.
- Identified trends using visualizations.
- Performed data preprocessing and analysis.
- Generated insights that can help businesses understand customer behavior.

---

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Clone this repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Narsimhabasa/Ecommerce-Customer-Behavior-Analysis.git
```

2. Install the required libraries

```bash
pip install pandas numpy matplotlib
```

3. Open the Jupyter Notebook and run all cells.

